      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Hisham Bin Al Musna, from Sadeyr, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Begin with Makkah and end with us<sup>asws</sup> (at Al-Medina)’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "1. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Hisham ibn af-Muthanna’ from Sadir who has said the following: “Abu ‘ Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said that you should commence with Makkah and end with us.” "
        ]
      }
